            <div class="title">
                Supplies And Services (Transitional Powers) Bill (Procedure)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1947-08-07/debates/7e6307bf-9e55-4915-bead-eb16985b6c5e/RoyalNavy(BoyEntrants)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
